    #1              This is a warrant canary.
───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

The existence of this canary means that no warrants have ever been
served to us with regard to the taskhive project (e.g. to hand out the
private signing keys, to introduce backdoors, or to release any data).

───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────






