  #6                  Privacy Seppuku Pledge
───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

Privacy and security are of the utmost importance to taskhive
developers. In the event we are compromised in a way we cannot alert
the public, we pledge to commit project seppuku and cease all
operations and development in accordance with the tradition set forth
by privacy conscious organizations.

